title: Kid Made Modern Hanukkah Craft Party
description:
Celebrate the festival of lights with our Hanukkah Craft Party! Everything you need to build a variety of joyful decor and gifts to create lasting memories. A perfect holiday gift for your favorite crafter. Recommended for ages 6 and up. Includes:

  • 12 felt shapes
  • 40 assorted pom poms
  • 15 fuzzy sticks
  • 20 googly eyes
  • 8 paper tubes
  • 10 star beads
  • 20 metallic pony beads
  • 33 assorted paillettes
  • 40 glue dots
  • elastic cording
